{"tid":2445130,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"暗戀。。。呢個男仔鍾意我嗎？","createTime":"2021-03-13T11:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T08:53:07.000Z","uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a868512c0771558c912ffd74658340b60fe63dd6","tid":2445130,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"我最近新識左個男仔，識左大約4個月。最近一個月我地close左，了解多左，會一齊出去玩、睇戲、食飯。<br />\n我地好似做多左比較親密嘅野，佢一定會陪我做我想做嘅野、佢好鍾意同我一齊影相、我地平時搭地鐵，佢會輕輕扶住我條腰，仲企得好埋。我有試過餵佢食零食，佢無抗拒。我又有試探過佢鍾意咩女仔，我好似中左好多。<br />\n我就好鍾意呢個男仔，但唔知佢鍾唔鍾意我。各位認為點？呢個男仔對我有無feel? 我要點做先可以令佢最鍾意我多啲呢？<br />\n 請指點。"},{"pid":"9f8f15e8fb2ab3c6ff9197cdbcc8f0cbd64016b5","tid":2445130,"uid":173515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"野都扑埋啦呢個應該"},{"pid":"487563f3652a24f90694947808a538a247073290","tid":2445130,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10734b37195e834ffd14fec734562d5f242b729d","tid":2445130,"uid":69544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"直接表白"},{"pid":"f950bb483539ce6f7c088549c0f08d43ae7c1e61","tid":2445130,"uid":64345,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eMvG6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eMvG6O.png&h=f982ca51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c487ace2968fce7a8aa73bbb9788d22ecf5195b1","tid":2445130,"uid":61543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"xX?"},{"pid":"781acde4852d6bfec37e16e369942b2c8c0fbbab","tid":2445130,"uid":282490,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"做咁多親密野<br />\n佢應該表左白啦 ？<br />\n<br />\n仲未表白的話，一係怕羞 一係食家<br />\n<br />\n如果佢未表白但暗示想一齊扑野 = 佢只想呃蝦條<br />\n貪你乾淨 食到就會離開你<br />\n<br />\n利申：身邊唔少食家 佢地而家食女係會比人有